CircleShape - Class in ds.graphics
A derived class the extends Shape with circle objects that are specified by a radius and the base point at the center of the figure.

CircleShape(double, double, double, int) - Constructor for class ds.graphics.CircleShape
Creates an instance with center (x,y), radius r and color c.
